        <h2 class="section-title">Project Overview</h2>
        <p>The Internal Job Portal (IJP) is designed to revolutionize internal mobility by providing a user-friendly platform where employees can discover new career opportunities within the organization. By centralizing job postings, skills management, and application processes, IJP empowers managers, HR professionals, and employees alike.</p>
        <p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>
        <ul class="list-unstyled text-start ms-5">
            <li>🔹 <strong>Job Postings:</strong> Managers can easily post, update, and manage job openings.</li>
            <li>🔹 <strong>Skill Management:</strong> Employees can update their skills, and the platform intelligently matches them with job requirements.</li>
            <li>🔹 <strong>Seamless Application:</strong> Apply for jobs with a single click, track your application status, and receive timely notifications.</li>
            <li>🔹 <strong>Administration:</strong> Admins maintain job, skill, and employee records to ensure data integrity and security.</li>
            <li>🔹 <strong>Secure Access:</strong> Robust authentication ensures that only authorized personnel have access to sensitive information.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Leveraging a modern, clean design and intuitive navigation, IJP helps improve employee engagement and streamlines internal recruitment processes.</p>
